FTAO is at present not a member of any formal association/ federation or confederation. &#xd;
&#xd;
FTAO works closely with other NGOs and wider civil society loose networks related to the issue. This for example could be with Trade Unions, Cooperatives, ISEAL and NGOs working on trade and development issues. FTAO also closely works with local authorities committed to Fair Trade.

